## ğŸ“¦ **Optional Features**

### **Basic (No extras)**
```bash
pip install django-mg
```

### **E-commerce**
```bash
pip install "django-mg[money,filer]"
```

### **Content**
```bash
pip install "django-mg[ckeditor,taggit]"
```

### **Full Features**
```bash
pip install "django-mg[filer,money,ckeditor,taggit,autoslug]"
```

### **GUI Only**
```bash
pip install "django-mg[gui]"
```

